~ start_npc
NPC: Hello traveler! This is a peaceful village.
Player: Good to know. Do you have any quests?
NPC: Not today, unfortunately.
=> END

~ start_enemy
Enemy: Grrr... Why are you talking to me? I'm supposed to kill you!
- Threaten him
	Player: Step aside or feel my blade!
	Enemy: Ha! Show me what you've got!
- Reason with him
	Player: We don't have to fight.
	Enemy: ...Fine, but get out of my sight.
=> END